Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.31,0:00:10.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It might be hard to ride at first,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.10,0:00:13.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,but if you just learn the trick to \N keeping your balance, you’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.94,0:00:15.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Balance, you say...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.77,0:00:20.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,When you turn, you just gotta shift \N your body weight a little bit over to one leg.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.35,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.81,0:00:29.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It might not be smooth sailing \N right away...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.10,0:00:32.23,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I see. The trick’s pretty similar \N to taking the helm, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.23,0:00:33.40,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.85,0:00:39.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,No way! \N You learned that way too fast!{Didn’t you learn that way too fast?}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.77,0:00:43.52,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Well, that just goes to show \N how well you taught me, Ms. Haru{Honorifics note: Haru-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.06,0:00:47.52,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Todoggler! You’re here!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.48,0:00:56.02,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Now, now... \N Wait for me, Todoggler.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.02,0:00:57.98,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.98,0:01:01.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah, wait! Please don’t just \N go off on your own!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.48,0:01:05.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Sheesh! \N Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}, please wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.23,0:01:07.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Now what...?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.48,0:01:18.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.77,0:01:21.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Yes! Very good, Koiking!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.77,0:01:24.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,When did you teach \N Koiking party tricks?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.94,0:01:28.02,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Party tricks? \N Oh, you give me too much credit.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.52,0:01:32.06,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Anyone can do this if they know \N how to make use of Koiking’s talents.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.02,0:01:36.35,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Todoggler! \N You’ll soak me again!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.35,0:01:37.69,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,All right, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.02,0:01:40.69,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,No splashing water on Ms. Haru{Honorifics note: Haru-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.77,0:01:45.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry. Seems like it{dread Todoggler} got carried away \N from having too much fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.81,0:01:55.19,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,The water temperature might be \N a tad too low for Koiking...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.73,0:01:59.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Given today’s water temp, \N we might want to move them somewhere else.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.81,0:02:00.94,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Would that be okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.94,0:02:02.35,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.35,0:02:04.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah! I’ll help you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.60,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,No need to concern yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.52,0:02:11.27,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Todoggler! Take them downstream!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Counting on you, Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.81,0:02:36.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,He’s already acting like \N a proper team player!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Tyler{Honorifics note: Tyler-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.19,0:02:42.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Could you take over the job \N of educating Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san} for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.73,0:02:44.65,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Educating?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.65,0:02:47.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Why don’t you just have him \N look at what you usually do?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.65,0:02:50.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But I really don’t have \N much experience yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.94,0:02:54.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Which makes me think it’d be better \N to have him learn from your example.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.65,0:02:59.40,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Nah! Uncle used to be \N super scary back in the day.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.40,0:03:02.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,If he glares at me, \N I’ll freeze up on the spot!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.48,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,So there’s no way I could do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.15,0:03:10.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? H-He’s {\i1}that{\i0} scary?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.65,0:03:14.35,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,It’ll be fine, it’ll be fine! \N {\i1}You{\i0} won’t get yelled at.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.35,0:03:15.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.65,0:03:19.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,So, you take good care \N of Uncle for me, Coach Haru!{Honorifics note: So, you take good care of Uncle for me, Haru-senpai!}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Ms. Haru{Honorifics note: Haru-san}! \N What should we do next?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.56,0:03:26.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Th-This is tough...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.90,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,My, what a magnificent field!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.15,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Heyo, Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.69,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Hard at work, I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.69,0:03:40.15,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Whoa... Haru really {\i1}is{\i0} teaching you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.06,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Things going okay? \N Or is {\i1}she{\i0} causing {\i1}you{\i0} trouble?{gyaku ni meiwaku kakete nai = Are you not, quite contrary to being helped, actually having troubles caused?}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.06,0:03:46.15,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Far from it. \N I’m learning plenty!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.65,0:03:49.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I-I’m giving it my all...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.23,0:03:52.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Well then, Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}, \N should we help out in the field?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.81,0:03:53.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.69,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Ooh, you’ll help too?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.40,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,How diligent!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.90,0:04:16.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,A berry? Isn’t that nice?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.81,0:04:27.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Water! Water! Water, water!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.35,0:04:41.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The wind’s strong today, \N so let’s not light any bonfires, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.48,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’m just glad \N that didn’t turn into a big fire.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I am so sorry{I’m truly sorry}, Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.60,0:04:55.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I know there’s so much I need to teach you, \N but I just keep messing up{ myself}...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.27,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.27,0:04:57.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Koduck?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.44,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,What is it? Is it{dread Koduck} feeling unwell?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Alisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.15,0:05:11.98,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Firewood chopped!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.31,0:05:23.69,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,My little pal isn’t good at \N controlling its{dread Koduck} Mind Power.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.98,0:05:32.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,{\q2}So whenever it looks like it’s about to activate,\N I try to find something it can let the power out on.{Dread Koduck - Ugh, so many its, some of which are dread Koduck, others which are just "Koduck's Mind Power."}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.94,0:05:35.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,There’s been times where I was too slow, \N and it caused a huge ruck{us}—{trailing off}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.98,0:05:36.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,K-Koduck?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah! Not those!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.06,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Nice catch, Haru!
Comment: 10,0:05:59.23,0:05:59.23,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.23,0:06:09.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ohh, I’m hopeless!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.27,0:06:14.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Right? I was completely hopeless, \N wasn’t I, Koduck?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.85,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And here I wanted to \N act like a good coach{Honorifics note: And here I wanted to act like a good senpai}...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.60,0:06:24.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I thought for sure \N I’d grown a little bit more than that...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.69,0:06:28.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,At the end of the day, \N I’m just not cut out to teach.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’ll tell Ms. Watanabe{Honorifics note: Watanabe-san} and have \N someone else take over from this afternoon!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yeah{Right}! That’s what I’ll do!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.02,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Oh, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I mean it! \N I was honestly impressed!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.77,0:06:43.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Um, Ms. Watanabe{Honorifics note: Watanabe-san}... \N I’d like to ask you{ something}...{Trailing off.}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.19,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Ah, Ms. Haru{Honorifics note: Haru-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.69,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,We were just talking about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.02,0:06:53.35,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I-I’m sorry! \N I’m sure I must have been a bother...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.35,0:06:58.35,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all! I was telling them \N how admirably you do your work!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.35,0:07:04.35,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,B-But all I’ve done today is trip, get splashed, \N drop berries... Absolutely nothing worth...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.35,0:07:09.10,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I never would’ve thought someone would be \N {\i1}that{\i0} direct in dealing with Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.94,0:07:17.19,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I’m certain that’s why Koduck trusts you so much, \N and always stays by your side!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.52,0:07:19.19,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Well, it’s true...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.19,0:07:23.98,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,...that Haru caused no end of trouble \N together with Koduck when she first got here...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.98,0:07:27.40,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,But she’s gotten way more calm \N and relaxed these days. Not to mention capable!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.10,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.10,0:07:34.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I never thought I’d get to \N hear you praise me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.15,0:07:38.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I-I’m kinda happy, \N but this is so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.94,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t have praised you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.94,0:07:44.44,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,It may be difficult for me \N to become quite like you,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,but I’ll work hard \N with that goal in mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,G-Goal?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.52,0:07:51.48,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,We’re counting on you \N as his coach.{Honorifics note: We’re counting on you, Haru-senpai.}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.48,0:07:53.10,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Good luck this afternoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.10,0:07:56.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? Ah... Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.35,0:08:01.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Uhh... This morning, \N we went from here to here, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,We had a look at the field, too, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}! Next up...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.77,0:08:13.94,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.94,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Dedenne! You’re here too?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.90,0:08:24.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.85,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh, I’m so sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.65,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t be playing around \N while I’m at work!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I took plenty of photos \N when I first got here, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.60,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.56,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Well, you don’t get to \N see a Kabigon all too often,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.40,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,so I was really happy \N to get a shot of it with Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.73,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Here, have a look!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.73,0:08:46.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh! You’re right! \N They’re adorable!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.77,0:08:49.10,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,There are so many Pokémon \N I’ve never seen before...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.10,0:08:53.44,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Do you mind if \N I send this to my son and his wife?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah... Well, no, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.48,0:08:57.85,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,They said they’d come visit \N one of these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.48,0:09:00.94,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Huh? That’s weird. \N I’m not getting a signal...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.94,0:09:03.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The signal’s bad on this island.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.98,0:09:08.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I was running around trying to get a signal too, \N back when I first got here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.85,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.06,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,That’s a shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.65,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Somebody help!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.27,0:09:18.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Alisa? Let’s move!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.02,0:09:18.94,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.48,0:09:38.15,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Hey, I said stop! Sheesh!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.81,0:09:40.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.06,0:09:43.98,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,They were just playing around at first, \N but now they’ve gotten really riled up...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.90,Main,Haru & Alisa,0,0,0,,Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.10,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Todoggler?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.40,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.40,0:10:22.69,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Quit your squabbling!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.65,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Well? I want you to make up!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}... really {\i1}is{\i0} terrifying, huh...?{Ergo "Well I didn't believe it when Tyler said he was super scary, but now I've seen it for myself and okay, he was right all along."}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.81,0:10:45.40,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Totally wild...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.98,0:10:49.10,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Oh... I was better at that \N when I was younger,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.73,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,but I hope I was some help, \N nonetheless.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.27,0:10:55.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yes... Glad you were here...{More literally "You are dependable"}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.02,0:10:55.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It’s just...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.90,0:11:00.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It looks like \N you’ve scared everyone stiff.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.06,0:11:06.06,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I-I’m so sorry! \N I didn’t mean to...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.31,0:11:12.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Next, let’s play with the Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.35,0:11:21.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wow! Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san} and Todoggler \N are doing something that looks really fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.69,0:11:24.10,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,All right! Here I go, Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.10,0:11:24.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.02,0:11:28.06,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Yes! Very good!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.06,0:11:34.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,‘Kay, let’s all give it a try!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.23,0:11:40.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Here I go, Koduck!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.31,0:11:49.10,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh...? How come?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.69,0:11:52.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}! \N Once more, if you would!{Intentional scenebleed}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.98,0:11:53.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,‘Course.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.85,0:12:02.98,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Whoa, amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.73,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,You want to try, Eevee?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.98,0:12:14.73,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.23,0:12:18.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,{\an8}Incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.23,0:12:19.48,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Well done, Eevee!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.52,0:12:24.19,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Man... It never would’ve turned out \N this well if {\i1}I{\i0} was in charge of him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.19,0:12:27.60,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Ms. Watanabe{Honorifics note: Watanabe-san}, did you have Haru train him \N ‘cause you {\i1}knew{\i0} it’d go like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.69,0:12:31.40,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,There are some things \N only Ms. Haru{Honorifics note: Haru-san} can do.
Comment: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:47.56,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}For so long, I’d been looking for you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:52.27,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}And at last, I found you on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:58.23,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}What a beautiful sunset this is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:03.10,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I’m glad I got to see it with you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.98,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When I was alone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.73,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When I felt lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:13.35,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}I would think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:19.19,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}Teach me, and only me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:24.23,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Those secret onomatopoeia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:29.27,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}Let me hear even more of them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:34.69,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}This is a healing island
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:37.31,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A spark-sparkly island
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:42.56,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Overflowing with fluff-fluffy love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:48.23,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Seeing you all shy, and just a bit embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:52.48,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I press my cheek against yours
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.94,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Time for a hug
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.23,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}(Time for a hug)
